An ambitious, well-rounded on-air personality, Lyndsay has more than ten years of experience in front of the camera and behind the scenes. Her background includes hosting, reporting, and producing for FOX Sports Network, Big Ten Network, Comcast SportsNet, CBS Boston, FOX Chicago, and the CW Network.
